Question: The left side has more people in the barber shop because there right side has zero people.

Reference Answer: False

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many people are in the barber shop on the left side?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many people are in the barber shop on the right side?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} > {ANSWER1}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
